c: 18
v: 17
t: "SÎṁ awia no pue a wobehu sÎṁ efri wÍṠn bodan no so rekÍṠ nifa soÍṠ, na sÎṁ ÎṁrekÍṠtÍṠ a etwam san wÍṠn ho kÍṠ benkum so, aberÎṁ a wÍṠn wÍṠ (ÍṠbodan no) mu wÍṠ baabi a ÎṁhÍṠ baeÎṁ. Woi yÎṁ NyankopÍṠn nsÎṁnkyerÎṁnee. Obia NyankopÍṠn atene no no ÍṠne obi a wanya kwankyerÎṁ, na obi a ÆbÎṁyera no no, onnya okyitaafoÍṠ a ÍṠbÎṁkyerÎṁ no kwan"